<div id="forgot-password" v-cloak>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="text-center">忘记密码</h1>
    <div class="forgot-form" v-if="!cloudSuccess">
      <p class="text-center">为重置帐户密码，请在下方输入您的电子邮件地址。</p>
      <hr/>
      <ajax-form action="sendPasswordRecoveryEmail" :syncing.sync="syncing" :cloud-error.sync="cloudError" @submitted="submittedForm()" :handle-parsing="handleParsingForm">
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="email" name="email-address" class="form-control" placeholder="sturgeon@example.com" :class="[formErrors.emailAddress ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="formData.emailAddress" autocomplete="email" focus-first>
          <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.emailAddress">请输入有效的电子邮件地址。</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-danger" v-if="cloudError"><small>处理您的请求时发生错误。 请检查您的信息，然后重试。</small></p>
        <div class="form-group">
          <ajax-button type="submit" :syncing="syncing" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block">发送重置链接</ajax-button>
        </div>
      </ajax-form>
      <p class="text-center"><a href="/login">回到登录页</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="success-message" v-if="cloudSuccess">
      <p>我们已向您发送了一个重置密码的链接。</p>
      <hr/>
      <p>如果几分钟后仍未收到电子邮件，请尝试检查您的垃圾邮件文件夹。 如果仍然找不到，请重试。</p>
      <p class="text-center"><a class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/login">回到登录页</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%- /* Expose locals as `window.SAILS_LOCALS` :: */ exposeLocalsToBrowser() %>
